statements.sql: select CONCAT(administrata.emri,' ',administrata.mbiemri) as prof, `lendet`.`Emri` as `lenda`, `lendet`.`idl` as `idl` from `vijushmeria` inner join `administrata` on `administrata`.`uid` = `vijushmeria`.`professor` inner join `lendet` on `lendet`.`idl` = `vijushmeria`.`idl` where `studenti` = '1447' and `vijushmeria`.`deleted` = '0' group by `vijushmeria`.`idl`

select CONCAT(administrata.emri,' ',administrata.mbiemri) as prof, `lendet`.`emri` as `lenda`, `lendet`.`idl` as `idl`, `raporti_notave_student`.`nota` as `nota` from `student_lendet` inner join `lendet` on `lendet`.`idl` = `student_lendet`.`idl` inner join `raporti_notave_student` on `raporti_notave_student`.`idl` = `student_lendet`.`idl` inner join `administrata` on `administrata`.`uid` = `student_lendet`.`prof` where `student_lendet`.`deleted` = '0' and `raporti_notave_student`.`locked` = '0'
